                                THE GOVERNMENT SHUTDOWN: A HISTORIC LESSON FOR PERSONAL FINANCE
                            </asp:HyperLink>
						</div>
                        <small class="post_meta">By R. David Michaels - Published February 1, 2019</small>
						<p class="card-text blog-description-text">
                            The government shutdown is a financial lesson for them and us. It is human nature to get 
                            comfortable with our way of life, don't forget to plan ahead.
						</p>
					</div>
